Description: The RDF book mashup demonstrates how Web 2.0 data sources like Amazon- Google or Yahoo can be integrated into the Semantic Web. The RDF book mashup makes information about books- their authors- reviews- and online bookstores available on the Semantic Web. This information can be used by RDF tools and you can link to it from your own Semantic Web data.
